# Indicators of Compromise (IoCs)

An **IoC (Indicator of Compromise)** is evidence that a system may have been compromised.

Common IoCs:
- File Hash (MD5 / SHA256)
- Malicious IP Address
- Malicious Domain
- File Name
- Registry Key
- Mutex
- Process Name

IoCs are imported into SIEMs, Firewalls, EDRs, and IDS/IPS solutions to automatically detect or block known threats.
